{
  "stem": "6195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There was a-- a lot has happened before that too, but I don't think we can talk about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, finally, I got through, and I met someone that knew someone, and that someone had some ways to get to the-- where they were assigning the rooms.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got a tiny little room where I was able-- I had to run back to Cracow, get my brother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sister was-- yeah, she came back to help me to pack, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- this man that was transferring our things, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was bringing the things into this room.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The room was the size, if you take from here to there, half of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so, he-- my father's library, not complete because when they saw, when the Nazis, the SS people, saw, at one stage, that he has a, a book printed in the-- Gutenberg printer.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, they had taken a few of those antiques.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the rest I try to save for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was the primary thing, and then I-- sheets and, like, linen and something to wear and pictures.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the man brought it to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I needed a wardrobe-- that was a problem-- which we had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or was it in there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a white one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, we wouldn't have it in the home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It must have been there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this three-door or four-door wardrobe, it took the whole wall, has taken the books, not the German books.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't care about the German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just my father's, what was precious to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wanted to make home.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
